subject: New to Eclipse
msgSnippet: Hi, I am new to using Eclipse. I am trying to run a java program using Eclipse but this is the error that I am getting. Exception in thread main
messageBody:
Hi,

I am new to using Eclipse. I am trying to run a java
program using Eclipse but this is the error that I am
getting.

Exception in thread "main" java.lang.Error: Unresolved
compilation problem:

at pfolder.StackParser.main(StackParser.java:1)

I tried compiling this program on the command prompt ,
outside the Eclipse environment and it compiled
without any errors.
What could be the reason for this error with Eclipse?


Thanks,
Prajakta
